title: O'Neill CWC South Africa '10 - FINAL
description: South African Greg Emslie wins the O'Neill Cold Water Classic South Africa 2010 ahead of Australian Dion Atkinson. In 4 ft. 4ft, sunny and windy conditions at Longbeach.
